  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They are-- they're doing what they have to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But you'll see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We'll get there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We'll-- we'll probably have to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we are strong and young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we'll work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And soon enough, it will be over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And Daddy will be at the gates waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So you know, that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the reason it took such a long time to go to-- we didn't know our destination-- which through Czechoslovakia to go to Auschwitz, Poland, shouldn't have taken that long time-- was that very many times, they just pushed us off to another track.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the-- the cars-- just the railroad just sat-- sat there on the tracks for overnight or a day or two.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we had no idea what's going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
